      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BALI UNLEASHED (1) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 0.8 lengths away in third (23.33) behind Just Rylee at this track. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Overdue and gets her chance. HIGH CUBE (4) was below best at his last start when 6th at this track following a win (23.07) there two back. Solid record here at this trip including 12 wins. Goes very well from this draw with four wins and two minor placings from 10 starts. Must be included in calculations. DIMORA BERNIE (6) is a super consistent dog who rarely misses the frame, last start scoring at this track (17.76), making it two straight wins. Has a good overall strike-rate and can find the frame here. CHUCK A PARTY (8) saluted last start after racing on the speed. That form reads well.",
